com.basho.riak.client.api

Class RiakCommand<T,S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.basho.riak.client.api.RiakCommand<T,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The response type
    S - The query info type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CoveragePlan, CoveragePlan, CreateTable, Delete, DeleteIndex, DeleteValue, DescribeTable, Fetch, FetchBucketProperties, FetchDatatype, FetchIndex, FetchSchema, FetchValue, ListBuckets, ListKeys, ListKeys, MapReduce, MultiDelete, MultiFetch, Query, ResetBucketProperties, Search, SecondaryIndexQuery, Store, StoreBucketProperties, StoreIndex, StoreSchema, StoreValue, UpdateDatatype, UpdateValue

    public abstract class RiakCommand<T,S>
extends Object
    The base class for all Riak Commands.

    All the commands the RiakClient can execute extend this class.

    Client Commands

    Fetching, storing and deleting objects

    • FetchValue
    • MultiFetch
    • StoreValue
    • UpdateValue
    • DeleteValue

    Listing keys in a namespace

    • ListKeys

    Secondary index (2i) commands

    • RawIndexQuery
    • BinIndexQuery
    • IntIndexQuery
    • BigIntIndexQuery

    Fetching and storing datatypes (CRDTs)

    • FetchCounter
    • FetchSet
    • FetchMap
    • UpdateCounter
    • UpdateSet
    • UpdateMap

    Querying and modifying buckets

    • FetchBucketProperties
    • StoreBucketProperties
    • ListBuckets

    Search commands

    • Search
    • FetchIndex
    • StoreIndex
    • DeleteIndex
    • FetchSchema
    • StoreSchema

    Map-Reduce

    • BucketMapReduce
    • BucketKeyMapReduce
    • IndexMapReduce
    • SearchMapReduce

    Since:
    2.0
